{"tid":686063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【估國家】鴨爸爸帶鴨仔過馬路，女司機照樣開車碌死兩隻","createTime":"2018-06-01T03:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T10:18:22.000Z","uid":29314,"like":12,"dislike":97,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"be529918384c7a70cd379aa26005d7e5b9e17864","tid":686063,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:02:41.000Z","msg":"英國一名母親帶著兩名年幼子女在麥當勞快餐店用餐時，目擊一名「邪惡」女司機在店外的外賣點餐車道，駕車輾過一群正在橫過車道的鴨子，當場壓死兩隻小鴨，覺得驚愕又憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n39歲的史密斯(Vicky Smith)日前帶著7歲兒子和5歲女兒在林肯郡斯凱格內斯(Skegness)一間麥當勞快餐台用餐，剛巧看到店外的外賣點餐車道。一名女子駕著「威龍」Megane房車在點餐窗口點了餐，此時剛巧有一群小鴨隨著鴨爸爸在車前橫過車道，但該女司機毫不理會，竟開車輾過鴨群到取餐窗口，頭也不回"},{"pid":"aaff210c41fc896154ab46b55c8aba6f606d0a24","tid":686063,"uid":51701,"like":148,"dislike":7,"score":141,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:06:40.000Z","msg":"祖國真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eab5028785f7b4b88100cd5f1546f45ee67b5b6","tid":686063,"uid":132038,"like":11,"dislike":111,"score":-100,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:06:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7e94d5e5fdec4cada2a6d6f8992c4e39442fe75","tid":686063,"uid":144843,"like":53,"dislike":2,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:07:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcddffa3b973f8d68ab9d9690bdf2a6734d7c173","tid":686063,"uid":48577,"like":55,"dislike":6,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"3eab5028785f7b4b88100cd5f1546f45ee67b5b6","tid":686063,"uid":132038,"like":11,"dislike":111,"score":-100,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:06:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:11:37.000Z","msg":"其實開車果個司機應該都係中國人"},{"pid":"f8de5b1478d1c3a913973c4f390e2e0fe7ec6dfe","tid":686063,"uid":185683,"like":45,"dislike":10,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:23:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0167b9a403ac4e92cc2835eb4442022d6b19cb19","tid":686063,"uid":511,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T03:34:14.000Z","msg":"睇唔到呀嘛，喺正㗎車前面?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"